rows.label: tlk45350153_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Someone remotely controlled
the Superbian Divine Beast itself!

rows.label: tlk45350153_03_msg0003
rows.name: I've never seen any technology like it!

rows.label: tlk45350153_03_msg0004
rows.name:
How in the world do you think
they did it?

rows.label: tlk45350153_03_msg0005
rows.name:
I wish I had even a fraction of that
technology. It would make controlling
Divine Beast weapons so much easier!

rows.label: tlk45350153_03_msg0006
rows.name:
It's too late for it now, but perhaps
we should have tried storming into
Acedia with Cetus!
